Package com.example.granny_gains_new.controller

Class StrengthController

java.lang.Object
com.example.granny_gains_new.controller.StrengthController
public class StrengthController extends Object
Controller class responsible for managing the strength training section of the fitness application. It handles workout favoriting, database interactions, UI updates, and scene navigation.

      Throws:

    • NavCardio

      Navigates the user to the Cardio screen.

    • NavStrength

      protected void NavStrength() throws IOException
      Navigates to the FitnessStrength.fxml scene when the NavStrength method is called. Retrieves the current Stage from the StrengthButton and loads FitnessStrength.fxml using FXMLLoader. Sets the scene with a width of 1200 and height of 700 to the retrieved Stage.
      Throws:
      IOException - if an input or output exception occurs during scene loading

    • NavHIIT

      protected void NavHIIT() throws IOException
      Navigates the user to the High-Intensity Interval Training (HIIT) screen. Loaded using FXMLLoader to display the FitnessHIIT.fxml file in a new Stage.
      Throws:
      IOException - if an error occurs while loading FitnessHIIT.fxml

    • handleBackToHome

      protected void handleBackToHome() throws IOException
      Handles the action to navigate back to the Home screen. Retrieves the current Stage from the HomeButton's Scene and loads the granny_gains_home.fxml file using FXMLLoader. Sets the scene with a size of 1000x1000 to the retrieved Stage.
      Throws:
      IOException - if an input or output exception occurred during scene loading
